title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Dec 15 2021

description:
Alex Berenson, author of Pandemia, joins us to discuss the latest covid madness, Omicron, and his potential lawsuit against Twitter. DeSantis on 700 days to stop the spread. SF Mayor suddenly wants to cut the bullcrap, stop crime. C&B take calls on covid mandates, transgender athletes. More Musk and Warren.
